---
title: Family Chicken Sausage Pizza Fun-Due 2x the delicious servings!
description: This crowd-pleasing pizza-style fondue is a fun, delicious way to gather family and friends around the table! You’ll combine crispy browned chicken sausage and tangy marinara with Italian cheeses in a creamy base, top with a shower of mozzarella, and pop it all in the oven until bubbly for a show-stopping presentation. Serve family style with veggies and toasty bread for dunking—don’t mind if we fon-due!

This recipe is double the typical servings, providing 4 servings and 8 servings for a 2 person and 4 person box respectively.
